GSD.description:
pinctrl: single: fix potential NULL dereference

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.1.12 by commit bcc487001a15f71f103d102cba4ac8145d7a68f2, it was introduced in version v4.11 by commit 571aec4df5b72a80f80d1e524da8fbd7ff525c98. For more details please see the references link.
